<p>As she crooned, the Wrecking Ball hitmaker sported a bold blue eyeshadow, cherry-hued lipstick and her short blonde tresses styled into an asymmetrical bob.  </p>

<p>'Watch out boy/ She'll chew you up (Oh-oh, here she comes)/ She's a maneater,' Cyrus cheekily sang, while swinging her microphone's stand with smoke up to her ankles. </p>

