<p>The former Disney star confirmed she and Simpson, whom she has known for a decade, called it quits on an Instagram Live clip in mid-August. </p>

<p>Referencing her split from ex-husband in August last year, Miley began: 'A year ago, almost to this exact date, the media tried to tell my story for me, and control my narrative, and I'm just not accepting that. </p>

<p>'So today, it came out that me and my boyfriend have broken up,' she continued. </p>

